contents:
[package]
authors = [ "Kofi Otuo <otuokofi@outlook.com>",]
name = "rifgen"
version = "0.1.7"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "swig", "java", "jni", "ffi", "cxx",]
repository = "https://github.com/Kofituo/rifgen"
license = "MIT"
description = "ffi Interface file generator. Use with flapigen"
readme = "README.md"
categories = [ "api-bindings", "development-tools", "development-tools::ffi", "development-tools::build-utils",]

[dependencies]
derive-new = "0.5"
Inflector = "0.11.4"

[dependencies.rifgen_attr]
path = "gen_attributes"
version = "0.1.0"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "full", "extra-traits", "derive",]

[dependencies.rifgen_attributes_utils]
path = "attributes_utils"
version = "0.1.0"
